text: Shock Treatment () is a 1973 French Italian drama movie directed by Alain Jessua and starring Annie Girardot, Alain Delon, Michel Duchaussoy, Robert Hirsch, Jeanne Colletin, Jean-François Calvé, Gabriel Cattand, Robert Party, Roger Muni. == Other websites == * Category:1973 drama movies Category:French drama movies Category:Italian drama movies Category:Movies directed by Alain Jessua
title: Shock Treatment (1973 movie)
